<emphasis bold="true" box="[485,576,874,899]" pageId="29" pageNumber="524">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
can be distinguished from other 
<taxonomicName box="[951,1063,875,899]" class="Insecta" family="Membracidae" genus="Allodrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="29" pageNumber="512" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
